detaileddescription.para: Function to try a few tricks to determine the displayed size of an img on the page. NOTE: This will ONLY work on an IMG tag. Returns FALSE on all other tag types.

simplesect.para: array an array containing the 'height' and 'width' of the image on the page or -1 if we can't figure it out.
